flowchart TD
    U[User input\npath + mode + optional format] --> P[file_open_info::parse\nsrc/Trajectory.cpp]
    P -->|format empty| G[guess_format(path, mode)\nsrc/guess_format.cpp]
    P -->|format provided| N[Trim format/compression]
    G --> X[Extension + compressed suffix\n.gz/.bz2/.xz]
    X --> Y[CIF vs mmCIF sniff\nfor read/append]
    Y --> E[FormatFactory::by_extension]
    N --> B[FormatFactory::by_name]
    E --> R[RegisteredFormat\ncreator + memory_stream_creator]
    B --> R
    R --> F[Concrete Format instance]
    F --> T[Trajectory holds unique_ptr<Format>]
